.name
WhereK
.description
A highly configurable hard drive utility.  Features an auto-
matic disk cataloger with 3 modes, turns directories into
ascii files that can be saved and searched, allows other
programs to run while continuing in the background, creates
lists with versions of the libraries on your hard drive and
disks.  All files created can be saved.  Features 2 help
modes, individual help for keys and a comprehensive help
mode, both accessible from the program.  
.short
Highly configurable hard drive utility.
.type
Disk Tool
.version
3.0
.exectype
Binary only
.distribution
Freeware
.requirements
WB 2.0+, WB 3.0 for Bulk Lister
.author  
Kenneth J. McCormick.
.described-by
David Zaroski (cz253@cleveland.freenet.edu)
